-- Datong Coal Posts 7.6% Increase in First-Quarter Net Income to $46 Million
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-04-21T23:41:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-21/datong-coal-posts-7-6-increase-in-first-quarter-net-income-to-46-million.html

          
          
             Datong Coal Industry Co.’s first
quarter net income rose 7.6 percent on a year earlier to 314
million yuan ($46 million).   
 The Chinese mining company’s sales rose 25 percent to 2.5
billion yuan, according to a statement to the Shanghai Stock
Exchange.   
 To contact the reporter on this story:
